This litte junction is an effective way of an U-turn.

[[File:en/Community/Junctionary/Mainline u turn.png|center|frame|U-Turn Junction]]

===Pros:===
*Cheap & small
*No sharp turns

===Cons:===
*Longer trains can block the mainline when in the turning lane - can be solved by making the turning lane long (though does have the side-effect of making the junction wider and thus taking up more space).

